ers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the game progresses, more and more monsters and powerful bosses will come to the battlefield. How to adjust your tactics in real time becomes the key to your survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726870/extras/98b04df2aab7246c6c99fe4a25df18ec.poster.avif?t=1768446747\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726870/extras/98b04df2aab7246c6c99fe4a25df18ec.webm?t=1768446747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726870/extras/98b04df2aab7246c6c99fe4a25df18ec.mp4?t=1768446747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726870/extras/5a52f1499a9f8655e16758d162b9bb1e.avif?t=1768446747\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726870/extras_big/5a52f1499a9f8655e16758d162b9bb1e.avif?t=1768446747 width=800 height=170 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will set off from a unique Main Base, defeat monsters as they move forward to randomly acquire a wide variety of items, and finally build their own genre system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vehicles and Synergies, Super Modules and Immediate Orders, random combinations will produce countless wonderful chemical reactions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every round was a new version that had never been seen before, and the rich Roguelike elements would make you never tired of playing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 + 1 > 2? 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 +... Of course it was infinite!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><